4. Bounded Context Architecture

System divided into 16 bounded contexts.

Core Contexts

Authentication

Responsibilities:

* OTP Login
* PIN
* Biometrics
* Device Approval

⸻

Customer

Responsibilities:

* Customer Profiles
* Aadhaar OCR
* PAN Management
* QR IDs
* Document Vault

⸻

Girvi

Responsibilities:

* Loan Creation
* Valuation
* KFS
* Payments
* Renewal
* Redemption
* Auction

⸻

Vault

Responsibilities:

* Locker Tracking
* Location Mapping
* Occupancy

⸻

Interest Engine

Responsibilities:

* Simple Interest
* Katmiti
* Daily Interest
* Penalties

⸻

Compliance

Responsibilities:

* RBI Rules
* Maharashtra Forms
* Annual Statements

⸻

Dashboard

Responsibilities:

* KPIs
* Alerts
* Exposure Metrics

⸻

Staff & RBAC

Responsibilities:

* Users
* Permissions
* Roles

⸻

Inventory

Responsibilities:

* Jewellery Inventory
* Barcode Tracking

⸻

Sales

Responsibilities:

* GST Billing
* Retail Sales

⸻

Purchase

Responsibilities:

* Scrap Gold Purchase

⸻

Savings Scheme

Responsibilities:

* Gold Savings Schemes

⸻

Reporting

Responsibilities:

* Financial Reports
* Compliance Reports

⸻

Settings

Responsibilities:

* Configuration
* Interest Setup
* Business Setup

⸻

Notifications

Responsibilities:

* Push Notifications
* WhatsApp

⸻

Backup & Sync

Responsibilities:

* Offline Sync
* Google Drive Backup

