6. State Management

Architecture:

BLoC Pattern

Each screen contains:

Screen
Bloc
Event
State
Repository
Datasource

Example:

CreateGirviScreen
CreateGirviBloc
CreateGirviEvent
CreateGirviState
GirviRepository
GirviRemoteDatasource
GirviLocalDatasource

⸻

7. Data Layer Architecture

Every repository uses:

Repository
       |
------------------
|                |
Remote         Local
Datasource     Datasource

Priority:

Read
Local First
Write
Local First
Sync
Background

⸻

8. Offline Architecture

Local Database:

SQLCipher SQLite

⸻

Sync States

PENDING
SYNCING
SYNCED
CONFLICT
FAILED

⸻

Sync Strategy

Write:

Device
   ->
Local DB
   ->
Sync Queue
   ->
Server

⸻

Conflict Strategy

Default:

Last Write Wins

Exception:

Financial Transactions

Must create Conflict Cards for Owner review.

⸻

